name: HyperlinkURLDestinations

properties.name: length
properties.description: The number of objects in the collection.

methods.name: add
methods.description: Creates a new hyperlink URL destination.

parameters.name: destination
parameters.description: The URL that the hyperlink points to. (Optional)

parameters.name: withProperties
parameters.description: Initial values for properties of the new HyperlinkURLDestination (Optional)

methods.name: count
methods.description: Displays the number of elements in the HyperlinkURLDestination.

methods.name: item
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkURLDestination with the specified index or name.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

methods.name: itemByName
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkURLDestination with the specified name.

methods.name: itemByID
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkURLDestination with the specified ID.

methods.name: itemByRange
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkURLDestinations within the specified range.

parameters.name: from
parameters.description: The HyperlinkURLDestination, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: HyperlinkURLDestination, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.description: The HyperlinkURLDestination, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: HyperlinkURLDestination, Long Integer or String.

methods.name: firstItem
methods.description: Returns the first HyperlinkURLDestination in the collection.

methods.name: lastItem
methods.description: Returns the last HyperlinkURLDestination in the collection.

methods.name: middleItem
methods.description: Returns the middle HyperlinkURLDestination in the collection.

methods.name: previousItem
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkURLDestination with the index previous to the specified index.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The index of the HyperlinkURLDestination that follows the desired HyperlinkURLDestination.

methods.name: nextItem
methods.description: Returns the HyperlinkURLDestination whose index follows the specified HyperlinkURLDestination in the collection.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The HyperlinkURLDestination whose index comes before the desired HyperlinkURLDestination.

methods.name: anyItem
methods.description: Returns any HyperlinkURLDestination in the collection.

methods.name: everyItem
methods.description: Returns every HyperlinkURLDestination in the collection.

methods.name: toSource
methods.description: Generates a string which, if executed, will return the HyperlinkURLDestination.
Returns the HyperlinkURLDestination with the specified index.

description: A collection of hyperlink URL destinations.
